body:
#### PR description:

The goal of this PR is a heavy refactoring of the package `CondTools/SiPixel`, as a follow-up of https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/35495.
   * plugin files have now class declarations within the implementation `.cc` file (headers are removed);
   * generalized modernization of the code where possible;
   * commit https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/36132/commits/16f73871383ab2740ed3b77b40ba8c6a60788023 migrates away from the deprecated `CondCore.DBCommon.CondDBCommon_cfi` includes;
   * commit https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/36132/commits/d83c502ae805b9869f8512b6f71eab432d1ae0b8  reduces the verbosity of CPE uploader configuration codes which were clogging the unit test logs.

#### PR validation:

Relies on existing unit tests.

